public Track[] getAlbumTracks(Album album,

                              int count,
                              int page)
                       throws JSONException,
                              WSError
从接口 JamendoGet2Api 复制的描述
Retrieve info on tracks from the given album using pagination. Tracks retrieved from given page will be appended to existing Album Tracks and whole list will be returned.

http://api.jamendo.com/get2/id+name+duration+url+stream/track/jsonpretty/?album_id=33

指定者：
接口 JamendoGet2Api 中的 getAlbumTracks
参数：
album - an Album instance
count - of items returned per page
page - number to retrieve count tracks from
返回：
a Track array from the given album
